data.description: This private home is located on a quiet 5 acres surrounded by trees, nearby lakes and rivers. The main level features 1 bedroom and bathroom, living room, kitchen/dining room with sliders to a large 14x36 covered deck overlooking the private yard. Downstairs, you have 2 bedrooms and a bathroom, laundry room, storage room and a living room. Outdoors, you will find a detached 3 stall garage and a 36 x 56 pole shed. Live within nature by sitting on the covered porch, or by enjoying the stars by a fire pit.
